<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Menilai <%= target.name %> - BEM Feedback</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #F3F4F6; }
        .fade-in { animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in; }
        @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4 md:p-6 fade-in pb-20">
    
    <div class="w-full max-w-xl">
        <div class="mb-6">
            <a href="/" class="text-gray-500 font-bold text-sm hover:text-blue-600 transition flex items-center gap-1">
                <span>←</span> Batal & Kembali
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100">
            
            <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 text-center text-white">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-slate-700 rounded-2xl mx-auto flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-bold mb-4 shadow-inner border border-slate-600">
                    <%= target.name.charAt(0) %>
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight"><%= target.name %></h1>
                <p class="text-slate-400 uppercase text-xs font-bold tracking-widest mt-2 bg-slate-800 inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-slate-700">
                    <%= target.role %> • <%= target.dept %>
                </p>
            </div>

            <form action="/rate" method="POST" class="p-6 md:p-8 space-y-8">
                <input type="hidden" name="target_nim" value="<%= target.nim %>">
                
                <% if(target.role === 'anggota') { %>
                    <input type="hidden" name="review_type" value="peer">

                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <label class="block font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg">1. Status Keaktifan</label>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3">
                            <label class="flex items-center p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl cursor-pointer hover:bg-blue-50 hover:border-blue-200 transition group">
                                <input type="radio" name="activity_status" value="aktif_tinggi" required class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 focus:ring-blue-500">
                                <span class="ml-3 font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-blue-800">🔵 Aktif Tinggi: Inisiatif tinggi, sering bantu teman, selalu on-track.</span>
                            </label>
                            <label class="flex items-center p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl cursor-pointer hover:bg-green-50 hover:border-green-200 transition group">
                                <input type="radio" name="activity_status" value="cukup_aktif" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 focus:ring-green-500">
                                <span class="ml-3 font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-green-800">🟢 Cukup Aktif: Aktif saat disuruh, tugas selesai, tapi jarang inisiatif.</span>
                            </label>
                            <label class="flex items-center p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl cursor-pointer hover:bg-red-50 hover:border-red-200 transition group">
                                <input type="radio" name="activity_status" value="pasif" class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 flex-shrink-0 focus:ring-red-500">
                                <span class="ml-3 font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-red-800">🔴 Pasif/Ghosting: Sering hilang, slow response, susah diandalkan.</span>
                            </label>
                            <label class="flex items-center p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 hover:border-gray-300 transition group">
                                <input type="radio" name="activity_status" value="unknown" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 focus:ring-gray-500">
                                <span class="ml-3 font-medium text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gray-800">⚪ Belum Pernah Kerja Bareng</span>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <label class="block font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg">2. Alasan/Bukti Nyata (Wajib)</label>
                        <textarea name="evidence" rows="3" required placeholder="Contoh: Pas proker X dia menghilang tanpa kabar..."
                            class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none transition"></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <label class="block font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg">3. Menurutmu, posisi dia semester depan sebaiknya gimana?</label>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <select name="recommendation" required class="w-full p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-300 focus:border-blue-500 outline-none bg-white appearance-none cursor-pointer">
                                <option value="" disabled selected>-- Pilih Rekomendasi --</option>
                                <option value="promosi">🚀 Pertahankan: Dia aset penting, kinerjanya top.</option>
                                <option value="evaluasi">⚠️ Butuh Evaluasi: Kerjanya oke, tapi ada sikap/komunikasi yang harus diperbaiki.</option>
                                <option value="rotasi">🔄 Rotasi: Kayaknya dia gak cocok di divisinya sekarang (salah tempat).</option>
                                <option value="reshuffle">🚪 Reshuffle: Maaf, kontribusinya sangat minim atau sifatnya toxic.</option>
                            </select>
                            <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 right-0 flex items-center px-4 text-gray-500">
                                <svg class="fill-current h-4 w-4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.293 12.95l.707.707L15.657 8l-1.414-1.414L10 10.828 5.757 6.586 4.343 8z"/></svg>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <label class="block font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg">4. Deskripsikan dia dalam 3 kata</label>
                        <input type="text" name="three_words" required placeholder="Contoh: Rajin, Pendiam, Lambat"
                            class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none transition">
                    </div>

                <% } else { %>
                    <input type="hidden" name="review_type" value="upward">

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        <div class="space-y-2">
                            <label class="block font-bold text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base">Seberapa jelas arahan & instruksi yang dia kasih?</label>
                            <select name="clarity_rating" required class="w-full p-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-300 focus:border-blue-500 outline-none bg-white">
                                <option value="5">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Sangat Jelas</option>
                                <option value="4">⭐⭐⭐⭐ Jelas</option>
                                <option value="3">⭐⭐⭐ Lumayan</option>
                                <option value="2">⭐⭐ Membingungkan</option>
                                <option value="1">⭐ Kacau</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div class="space-y-2">
                            <label class="block font-bold text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base">Seberapa support dia pas kamu ada masalah/bingung?</label>
                            <select name="support_rating" required class="w-full p-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-300 focus:border-blue-500 outline-none bg-white">
                                <option value="5">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Sangat Support</option>
                                <option value="4">⭐⭐⭐⭐ Support</option>
                                <option value="3">⭐⭐⭐ Biasa</option>
                                <option value="2">⭐⭐ Cuek</option>
                                <option value="1">⭐ Tidak Peduli</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <label class="block font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg">2. Bagaimana pola komunikasi saat ini?</label>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3">
                            <label class="flex items-center p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl cursor-pointer hover:bg-blue-50 hover:border-blue-200 transition group">
                                <input type="radio" name="comm_style" value="jernih" required class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 focus:ring-blue-500">
                                <span class="ml-3 font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-blue-800">🔵 Jernih: Arahan jelas, fast response, gak bikin bingung.</span>
                            </label>
                            <label class="flex items-center p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 hover:border-gray-300 transition group">
                                <input type="radio" name="comm_style" value="inkonsisten" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 flex-shrink-0 focus:ring-gray-500">
                                <span class="ml-3 font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900">⚪ Inkonsisten: Hari ini A besok B, arahan sering berubah mendadak.</span>
                            </label>
                            <label class="flex items-center p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl cursor-pointer hover:bg-orange-50 hover:border-orange-200 transition group">
                                <input type="radio" name="comm_style" value="slow" class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 focus:ring-orange-500">
                                <span class="ml-3 font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-orange-800">🟠 Slow/Bottleneck: Susah dihubungin, info sering mandeg di dia.</span>
                            </label>
                            <label class="flex items-center p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl cursor-pointer hover:bg-red-50 hover:border-red-200 transition group">
                                <input type="radio" name="comm_style" value="otoriter" class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 flex-shrink-0 focus:ring-red-500">
                                <span class="ml-3 font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-red-800">🔴 Otoriter: Suka nyuruh tanpa mau denger kendala di lapangan.</span>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <label class="block font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg">3. Apakah gaya kepemimpinan dia membuatmu termotivasi bertahan di sini?</label>
                        <div class="flex gap-4">
                            <label class="flex-1 text-center p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:bg-green-50 hover:border-green-200 cursor-pointer transition group">
                                <input type="radio" name="work_comfort" value="ya" required class="accent-green-600 w-5 h-5">
                                <div class="font-bold text-green-600 mt-2 group-hover:text-green-800">✅ Ya</div>
                            </label>
                            <label class="flex-1 text-center p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:bg-yellow-50 hover:border-yellow-200 cursor-pointer transition group">
                                <input type="radio" name="work_comfort" value="biasa" class="accent-yellow-500 w-5 h-5">
                                <div class="font-bold text-yellow-600 mt-2 group-hover:text-yellow-800">😐 Biasa</div>
                            </label>
                            <label class="flex-1 text-center p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:bg-red-50 hover:border-red-200 cursor-pointer transition group">
                                <input type="radio" name="work_comfort" value="tidak" class="accent-red-600 w-5 h-5">
                                <div class="font-bold text-red-600 mt-2 group-hover:text-red-800">❌ Tidak</div>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <label class="block font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg">4. Apa yang harus dia perbaiki/kurangi biar kementerian dapat berjalan dengan lancar dan gak chaos?</label>
                        <textarea name="feedback_essay" rows="3" required placeholder="Saran perbaikan..."
                            class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none transition"></textarea>
                    </div>
                <% } %>

                <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-slate-900 hover:bg-black text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg transition transform active:scale-[0.98] mt-6">
                    Kirim Penilaian 📨
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>